pageProduct.name: Orzene Keratin Power Conditioner 250ml
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Orzene Beer Keratin Power Conditioner for dry and damaged hair, helps the restoration of hair thanks to Keratin repair system, a specially developed system with yeast extract & keratin.
Enriched with Shine Elixir consisting of Beer, Ceramides and Phytoprotein  hydrates hair, enhances elasticity and shine, leaving hair with an airy feeling.

Directions

Apply on wet hair, massage gently and rinse thoroughly. For enhanced results, combine it with the rest ORZENE BEER KERATIN POWER products. In case of contact with eyes, rinse immediately with plenty of water.
